<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            /* White text */
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #444;
            /* White heading */
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .small-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <h1>Reset Password</h1>
        <p>
            You recently requested to reset your password for your account. Click the button below to reset it.
        </p>
        <a href="{{resetPasswordLink}}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
        <p class="small-text">
            If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or reply to let us know. This password
            reset is only valid for the next 24 hours.
        </p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2024 <a target="_blank" href="https://links.taptrick​.io">taptrick​.io.</a> All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>